S.FORM: 3EP-salunganay tatayna siwkay - angangan kalunasulitan: saayaway a nganan niza ci Zhou Youting周幼婷, ci Guo Tingting郭婷婷 atu ci Lin Weiling林韋伶. Amilika a ngangan niza, inayi' ku Amilika a ngangan. malimula' a ngangan niza , inayi' ku malimula a ngangan. u etul niza u tatana amin. nalecuhan, ci Zhou Youting 1977.6.10, ci Guo Tingting1978.11.4 atu ci Lin Weiling1980.2.1 . u kanatal kuheni sa, u ROC.Taywan. u cidekay kuheni sa, u Hulam. u kakawsan a enengan niza sa, kaaykatineng. u kulit nu banges niza sa, u takuliway. u kulit nu bukes niza sa, u lumeniay. u kawaw niza ayza sa, u palaway. u subana'ay niza sa, u tabakiay a cacudadan. kamu niza sa, u Hulam atu Amilika. - kawaw kalunasulitan: sadadiw kakuniza sa, u Hulam malikitay a dadiw. sadadiw sa, inayi'. patahkal a mihcan sa, 1998 a mihcan. patahkal a nalimaan sa, 3EP salungan tatayna a lais, natahkal i 1999.7.1. sakapahay a nalimaan sa, 3EP salungan tatayna a lais. tanitik a mihcan sa, u 1999 a mihcan. dadiw a kakawawan sa, u Gunse. mikuwanay a kakawawan sa, u Gunse. palaacawa niza sa, caayhenay. papazaan atu papayzaan niza sa, caaykatineng. takalaw niza sa, caaykatineng. baeked niza sa, caaykatineng. u kanamuhan niza sa,caaykatineng. - u nikauzip niza: Zhou Youting mipalaw i Binawlan Tilibi. Guo Tingting patahkal sakacacay a dadiw CD niza " u demec nu namuh" Lin Weiling mipalaw tu iga, maala ku kawlah ni iga, sakapahay baluhayay a tademaw nu iga, 2002 a mihcan tayza Korea mikawaw. - kakalimaan nazipa'an: - namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Apple-iTunes 3EP美少女介紹網頁 nasulitan nay pabalucu'ay a kawaw nu subana'ay a pu 2018-1

3EP-salonganay tatayna siwkay - angangan kalonasolitan: saayaway a nganan niza ci Zhoo Yooting周幼婷, ci Goo Tingting郭婷婷 ato ci Lin Weiling林韋伶. Goo Tingting patahkal sakacacay a dadiw CD niza " o demec no namoh" Lin Weiling mipalaw to iga, maala ko kawlah ni iga, sakapahay balohayay a tademaw no iga, 2002 a mihcan tayza Korea mikawaw. - kakalimaan nazipa'an: - namakayniay a nasolitan nasakamoan ato natinengan Apple-iTones 3EP美少女介紹網頁 nasolitan nay pabaloco'ay a kawaw no sobana'ay a po 2018-1
